title: The Service is Still Great, but the App Has Had Issues Lately
text:
Title says it all - I really enjoy the service and all of the music and pods it allows me to listen to. 

Lately though, the app stops playing music at random and when I go back into it and press play, nothing happens (I usually have to close/relaunch). It is not a huge problem in the grand scheme of things, but given that it happens multiple times per day and the fact music helps me avoid distractions during work (I have pretty severe ADHD), it is kind of a let down, especially since I am paying for a family plan on premium.

title: Will the Apple Watch app ever work?!
text: I have been a Spotify customer for years, I have an Apple Watch and download songs to play offline. To this day March 20, 2024 I have never been able to leave my phone behind, connect my AirPods to the Apple Watch and listen to downloaded songs while on a run. If I use allle music, guess what it works without issue. What is the point of an Apple Watch app to download songs to but never be able to use it when needed!!!! Frustrating to say the least!!!
